data.description: Welcome home! This spacious home is located in Palm Aire Village with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths plus a den , 2202 square feet of living space where the eat-in kitchen overlooks the dining area and beyond.  Located on a corner lot, with a deck that overlooks the play area and backyard with a shed.  Also, the one car garage can be used a as gym or other extra needed space.  New AC system and windows and doors.  Exterior of the home has been recently painted.  This home is truly amazing! Connect anytime for a private tour!  *White Samsung Washer does not convey
